   <h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold;\">Program Outline & Learning Objectives</h2>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0;\">\n      <li style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0 20px;\"><strong></strong> This program will help participants understand the basics of Linux OS and its applications in bioinformatics workflows, learn Bash scripting for automating NGS workflows, use Biopython and R programming for NGS data analysis and processing, perform Next Generation Sequencing (NGS) data analysis techniques, and apply bioinformatics tools for sequence alignment and variant calling.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n\n\n\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold;\">Training Format and Activities</h3>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0;\">\n    <li>Interactive lectures and presentations</li>\n    <li>Hands-on exercises for Linux OS and scripting</li>\n    <li>Practical demonstrations using Biopython</li>\n    <li>NGS data analysis workflow discussions</li>\n    <li>Assignments for participants</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold;\">Instructors</h3>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0;\">\n    <li>Bioinformatics Division, National Institute of Biotechnology (NIB)</li>\n  </ul>\n\n\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold;\">Program Schedule</h3>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: none; padding-left: 80px; margin-left: 80px;\">\n      <li style=\"text-align: left;\">Day 1: Introduction to Linux OS and its role in bioinformatics</li>\n      <li style=\"text-align: left;\">Day 2: Bash scripting for automation and task management</li>\n      <li style=\"text-align: left;\">Day 3: Python and Biopython for NGS data analysis</li>\n      <li style=\"text-align: left;\">Day 4: NGS workflows and data interpretation</li>\n      <li style=\"text-align: left;\">Day 5: Final project and hands-on NGS data analysis</li>\n  </ul>\n\n\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold;\">Duration & Location</h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Duration: 5 days <br> National Institute of Biotechnology (NIB), Dhaka, Bangladesh</p>\n\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n    <a href=\"https://nib.gov.bd\" class=\"btn btn-primary rounded-pill me-2\" style=\"padding: 15px 30px; font-size: .6em;\">Program Details</a>\n  </p>\n</div>\n`);\n</script>\n\n<!-- Add additional details if required -->\n<style>\n  #program-details {\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    color: #333;\n    line-height: 1.8;\n    padding: 100px; /* Added more padding on the left */\n    background-color: #f9f9f9;\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    font-size: 1.2em;\n  }\n  \n  h2, h3 {\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  ul ul {\n    margin-left: 60px; /* Increased indentation */\n  }\n\n  p {\n    font-size: 1.2em;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  /* Slideshow container */\n  .slideshow-container {\n    position: relative;\n    height: 100vh;\n    width: 100%;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  /* Each slide */\n  .mySlides {\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    background-size: cover;\n    background-position: center;\n    opacity: 0;\n    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;\n  }\n\n  .mySlides:first-child {\n    opacity: 1;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<script>\n  let slideIndex = 0;\n  const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.mySlides');\n  \n  function showSlides() {\n    slides.forEach((slide) => {\n      slide.style.opacity = '0';  // Hide all slides\n    });\n    slideIndex++;\n    if (slideIndex > slides.length) { slideIndex = 1; }  // Loop back to first slide\n    slides[slideIndex - 1].style.opacity = '1';  // Show the current slide\n    setTimeout(showSlides, 3000);  // Change image every 3 seconds\n  }\n\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n    s